{"tid":1647974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普：美國歡迎中國留學生，中國學生唔會畀區別對待","createTime":"2019-10-12T03:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T04:11:27.000Z","uid":313615,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bac764b80d170b1f340f3e43f827aa48e1c3a04a","tid":1647974,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:49:15.000Z","msg":"華盛頓&mdash;美國總統川普周五表示，美國歡迎中國留學生，中國學生唔會畀區別對待。<br />\n當記者提到中國學生面臨簽證變難局面嘅時候，川普對此表示唔認同，稱美國將對中國學生&ldquo;非常好&rdquo;。<br />\n川普話：&ldquo;我哋擁有世界上最優良嘅大學系統，我哋將繼續維持得個水平，之所以優良嘅其中一個原因嘅係我哋有好多嚟自中國嘅學生。我哋唔會將佢簽證變難，我哋將為所有人做到呢一D。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周五（10月11日）喺白宮會晤咗中國副總理劉鶴，除咗宣布貿易協議嘅第一部分將喺未來幾周完成之外，美國有計劃要將學校大門向中國關閉一事表示唔實傳言。佢補充，中國留學生唔會畀&ldquo;有咩唔同&rdquo;。「我哋將對中國學生好好&ldquo;，佢話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/VOAChinese/status/1182824367148933121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVOAChinese%2Fstatus%2F1182824367148933121&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=7a9f8fd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVOAChinese%2Fstatus%2F1182824367148933121&h=b1783598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/VOAChinese/status/1182824367148933121</a>"},{"pid":"6006f14cf5acfe6ae8ebce02379c7ff665ce08dd","tid":1647974,"uid":34602,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:52:29.000Z","msg":"習總是我的好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942d8b35e86f05e489ef9715b3e33efa70a84041","tid":1647974,"uid":105905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"佢既好好即係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8a83b0b119a4ad2c4723c47bd2492e4b192e7a","tid":1647974,"uid":227271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:57:43.000Z","msg